offer an array of services and information. 
</P>
<P>
 The fair, to be held today and Sunday at the Hyatt Newporter, will be a 
gathering place for palm readers, massage therapists and a wide variety of 
others who specialize in psychic phenomenon, said Kathleen Scott, a veteran 
astrologer from Newport Beach. 
</P>
