<TEXT>
<P>
 In other Division I matches: 
</P>
<P>
 Corona del Mar 3, Estancia 2 -- Brian Coleman had 19 kills and Brooks Hoppe 
had 17 kills to lead Corona del Mar, which won 15-7, 11-15, 15-11, 13-15, 15-5. 
The Sea Kings (15-2) will play top-seeded El Toro on Tuesday. 
</P>
