 Huntington Beach 3, Irvine 1 -- Brad Simons led Huntington Beach (17-2) with 
15 kills in a 15-8, 15-17, 15-12, 15-3 victory. Teammate Jeremy Bart added 13 
kills and Nick Ziegler had five blocks. The Oilers will play Manhattan Beach 
Mira Costa Tuesday. 
</P>
