 In Division II: 
</P>
<P>
 Esperanza 3, Redlands Arrowhead Christian 0 -- Third-seeded Esperanza (15-2) 
had no trouble defeating Redlands Arrowhead Christian 15-4, 15-3, 15-6. Senior 
Mike Allison had 20 kills to lead the Aztecs, who will play Canyon on Tuesday. 
</P>
<P>
 Los Amigos 3, Foothill 2 -- Brian Laske and Kiet Tran each had 33 kills to 
lead Los Amigos (14-1), 10-15, 15-13, 15-2, 3-15, 17-15. 
