Whittier Christian (13-3) to a 15-6, 15-9, 15-0 victory. Teammate Jason Hyde 
added eight kills and six digs and setter Chris Keife had 38 assists. Whittier 
Christian advances to play Santa Fe Springs St. Paul, which beat St. 
Margaret's, 15-9, 15-11, 15-12. Pius X finishes 8-7. 
</P>
<P>
 In a Division II boys' tennis wild-card match: 
</P>
<P>
 Esperanza 14 2/3, La Quinta 6 1/3 -- Devin Lopez swept at No. 1 singles, 6-0, 
6-2, 6-1, for Esperanza (12-9). The Aztecs will play at Downey in the first 
round Tuesday. 
</P>
<P>
 Laguna Beach 16 1/3, Los Amigos 4 2/3 -- Elliott West swept his sets, 6-0, 
6-0, 6-0, for the Artists. In doubles, Joe Redford and Ben Cohen swept their 
sets, 6-1, 6-1, 6-3. Laguna Beach (13-7) will play at Los Alamitos in the first 
round Tuesday. 
</P>
<P>
 In a Division III boys' tennis wild-card match: 
</P>
<P>
 Western 12 1/3, Walnut 8 2/3 -- Dean Raf swept in singles, 6-1, 6-2, 6-2, for 
visiting Western (10-9), which advances to play Burbank in the first round. 
Anthony Nguyen also won his singles sets, 6-4, 7-6, 7-6. 
</P>
