<TEXT>
<P>
 What a great story about disabled actor Richard Robert Redlin appearing in 
"Hart to Hart."("Richard Robert Redlin Looks Forward to a Different Role," May 
6). From my experience as an extra, I do think terrible, old barriers are being 
torn down. 
</P>
