directors from putting me in scenes with Warren Beatty, Robert Wagner, Danny 
Aiello and Connie Sellecca. 
</P>
<P>
 Let me tell you, there are few greater triumphs than a director looking across 
a sea of extras and picking a disabled person to do a scene. 
