MAN, 42, FOUND DEAD IN HIS HOME 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 A 42-year-old man was found dead in his home in an upscale neighborhood Friday 
morning, Los Angeles police said. 
</P>
<P>
 The cause of death was not disclosed, but detectives from the Los Angeles 
Police Department's Devonshire Division are working with investigators from the 
department's Robbery-Homicide Division on the case, said Officer John Lopata. 
</P>
<P>
 Police withheld the man's name. 
