Charlene Love and James Gates for "Sin for a Season" and Christina Cottles for 
"Serenity," all from Los Angeles; Kenneth Gay of San Quentin for "A Children's 
Story" and Rosa Graham of Chicago for "Lonely Street." 
</P>
